<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/footer.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/library-profile.css" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/vxnhe-icon.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-DTOQO9RWCH3ppGqcWaEA1BIZOC6xxalwEsw9c2QQeAIftl+Vegovlnee1c9QX4TctnWMn13TZye+giMm8e2LwA=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <script defer src="/js/homepage.js"></script>
    <title>Library Profile</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials_readers/head_navigation.ejs'), { user: user } %>
    <a href="/library-profile/>"></a>
    <div id="upper" class="pt-9">
        <div id="banner" class="border-4 top-9 relative h-96 mx-20 my-5 rounded-lg"> 
            <div class="absolute w-full h-full">
                <img class="h-full w-full" src="/<%= library.banner %>" alt=" Library's Banner">
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-32 left-36 flex items-center">
               <div id="lib-ava" class="rounded-full overflow-hidden border-8 border-y-"> 
                    <img src="/<%= library.profilePicture %>" alt="<%= library.username %>'s Picture Profile">
                </div> 
                <div id="lib-info" class="mt-32 ml-10">
                    <div id="lib-username">Library name: <%= library.username %></div>
                    <div id="lib-address">Address: <%= library.address %> address </div>
                    <div id="lib-email">Email: <%= library.gmail %></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="lower" >
        <div id="book-container" class="border-4 border-red-800 mx-20 my-60" >
            <div class="book-card m-6">
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Blanditiis tempore repellendus iusto nam suscipit reprehenderit, nobis tempora maxime soluta aliquid culpa incidunt! Voluptates doloribus, cupiditate aspernatur ullam quis dicta consequatur.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- <%- include('../partials_readers/footer.ejs') %> -->
</body>

</html>